    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "You sound so certain of it... as if the darkness truly has a place for me. But the world feels so heavy, so loud and cruel, and I am just so tired of fighting to stay upright. Is it really wrong to want to just let go? To believe that my departure would be a mercy to everyone?",
